d withdrawal of consent by individuals</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2\"> </a></td><td>Healthcare providers</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.1<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.461\"> </a></td><td>Identification and registration of persons</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.1.1<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.461.461\"> </a></td><td>Verify a person's unique identity</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.1.2<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.461.462\"> </a></td><td>Enrol person(s) for health services/clinical care plan</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.2<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.462\"> </a></td><td>Person-centred health records</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.2.1<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.462.461\"> </a></td><td>Longitudinal tracking of person's health status and services</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.2.2<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.462.462\"> </a></td><td>Manage person-centred structured clinical records</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.2.3<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.462.463\"> </a></td><td>Manage person-centred unstructured clinical records (e.g. notes, images, documents)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.2.4<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.462.464\"> </a></td><td>Routine health indicator data collection and management</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.3<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.463\"> </a></td><td>Healthcare provider decision support</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.3.1<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.463.461\"> </a></td><td>Provide prompts and alerts based according to protocol</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.3.2<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.463.462\"> </a></td><td>Provide checklist according to protocol</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.3.3<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.463.463\"> </a></td><td>Screen persons by risk or other health status</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">2.4<a name=\"zh-CDHIv2-2.464\"> </a></td><td>Telemedicine</td></tr><tr><