  fhir:description [ fhir:v "CodeSystem for the Classification of Digital Interventions, Services and Applications in Health\n(CDISAH), second edition (2023). ISBN 978-92-4-008194-9.\n\nOrganised into four groups based on the primary user:\n  1. Persons\n  2. Healthcare providers\n  3. Health management and support personnel\n  4. Data services\n\nNew categories vs v1: 1.4.4, 1.6.2, 1.8, 2.5.6, 2.11, 3.1.5, 3.5.7, 3.5.8, 3.8, 4.3.5, 4.4.2, 4.4.3, 4.5.\nSee ConceptMap CDHIv1toCDHIv2 for the full mapping from the first edition."] ; # 
